        .. _makinacom:  http://www.makina-corpus.com
        
        
        Dependencies
        ============
        
        * Plone
        * p4a.videoembed
        
        Why this package ?
        ==================
        
        p4a.plonevideoembed depends on p4a.video that has too much dependecies and too
        much features (subtype, metadata, ...).
        
